{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"おつかれさまでした！(おつかれさまでした — Good work!) Here's what was implemented:\n\n**New modules:**\n- **`src/amp/state.rs`** — State file (`~/.local/share/ishi/state.json`) mapping issue identifiers to Amp thread IDs, with load/save/link operations\n- **`src/amp/thread.rs`** — Reads Amp thread JSON files from `~/.local/share/amp/threads/`, extracting title, message count, and last activity time (with relative time formatting)\n\n**Updated files:**\n- **`src/app.rs`** — Added `DetailSection` enum (Body/Threads), thread state fields, and navigation methods (`thread_move_down/up`, `focus_threads/body`)\n- **`src/views/detail.rs`** — Renders \"Threads (N)\" section below comments with highlighted selection, cyan border on focused section, and context-aware status bar\n- **`src/keys.rs`** — Added `Tab` and `NewThread` (`a`) key actions\n- **`src/main.rs`** — Wired thread loading on issue select, Tab to switch sections, j/k for thread navigation\n\n**Tests:** 70 tests passing (added 12 new tests covering state persistence, thread parsing, timestamp conversion, relative time formatting, and thread navigation)."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":609,"cache_read_input_tokens":103441,"output_tokens":320,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff5d-cbf9-76ae-ba67-6f6c84c089e3"}
